1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,691
The first few feet outside should
feel calm, not complicated.

2
00:00:04,178 --> 00:00:07,272
Smooth power helps every start
feel more natural.

3
00:00:07,815 --> 00:00:11,104
Steady support can turn a doorway
into a real beginning.

4
00:00:11,793 --> 00:00:14,246
Because dignity should never stay
indoors.
